The worst is when you're teaching C and you have to explain that<p><pre><code>    void * a = do_something1(do_something2(), do_something3());
</code></pre>
is not equivalent to<p><pre><code>    int b = do_something2();
    int c = do_something3();
    void * a = do_something1(b, c);</code></pre>
